{"tid":1738973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共一定唔會取消區選 呢幾日劇本就係為左 total win","createTime":"2019-11-19T12:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T13:44:40.000Z","uid":105995,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"98f743b79783269f1492a1dea6c8bd52ff5efd58","tid":1738973,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"區選作為一個全港大型公投<br />\n<br />\n一旦中共贏左 會大舉增加藍絲氣焰 <br />\n<br />\n示威者變成小眾 失去民意授權嘅合法性 黑警更加會肆無忌憚攻擊示威者<br />\n<br />\n對內中共又有大把材料做維穩<br />\n<br />\n外國傳媒見到香港民意係藍絲度 未必會咁積極幫香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對中共係千載難逢反cup嘅機會</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">贏就贏間廠 輸只需繼續封鎖消息 睇唔到任何原因取消區選</span><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日故意激法衝突 就係為咗製造社會混亂嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n增加藍絲，同埋特別係政治冷感嘅人嘅投票率 <br />\n<br />\n加上大量三毛吹奏無差別攻擊 帶風向<br />\n<br />\n又派大量鬼混入示威者裏應外合<br />\n<br />\n目的好明顯就係為咗增加中共勝算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以大家呢段時間 要保持獨立思考</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中共一定仲有好多手段 而家先係開始 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b3c4ac995edc5b8ac15f9c220fecc57ff5a9a8","tid":1738973,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15870d4047d1ea3c01795f48e9da5964fd79cdf1","tid":1738973,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"75bfe789d6e9d03c0e4a7fa147049ad92a7126fc","tid":1738973,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n另外，一番肺腑連同深度分析，大家都可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738105/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8fbb6b98375ea5ee4005ac7f993b4dff12fa74ea","tid":1738973,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75bfe789d6e9d03